OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773137102
OL,3,CLiverpool and Manchester United
OL,4,Ccomplain to X over 'sickening' AI posts
OL,6,FManchester United and Liverpool FC
OL,7,Fhave complained to social media site X
OL,8,Fover a number of AI generated posts
OL,9,Fthat make offensive and incorrect
OL,10,Fclaims about the Munich Air Disaster
OL,11,Fand the Hillsborough Disaster.
OL,13,FThe posts were made by the social
OL,14,Fmedia site's AI chatbot Grok in
OL,15,Fresponse to prompts from users asking
OL,16,Fit to make "vulgar" and "offensive"
OL,17,Fcomments.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773137102
OL,3,CLiverpool and Manchester United
OL,4,Ccomplain to X over 'sickening' AI posts
OL,6,FOne post blamed Liverpool fans for the
OL,7,F1989 Hillsborough Disaster which which
OL,8,Fled to the deaths of 97 football fans
OL,9,Fat the FA Cup semi-final between
OL,10,FLiverpool and Nottingham Forest.
OL,12,FPolice initially blamed Liverpool
OL,13,Fsupporters for causing the disaster
OL,14,Fbut, after decades of campaigning by
OL,15,Ffamilies, that narrative was debunked.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773137102
OL,3,CLiverpool and Manchester United
OL,4,Ccomplain to X over 'sickening' AI posts
OL,6,FOther posts included offensive
OL,7,Fcomments about the death of Diogo Jota
OL,8,Fand the 1958 Munich Air Disaster; a
OL,9,Fplane crash in which 23 people died
OL,10,Fincluding eight Manchester United
OL,11,Fplayers.
OL,13,FBoth clubs have complained to the Elon
OL,14,FMusk-owned platform, which has since
OL,15,Ftaken down the posts.
OL,17,FLiverpool MP Ian Byrne has said the
OL,18,Fcomments are "appalling and completely
OL,19,Funacceptable".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773137102
OL,3,CLiverpool and Manchester United
OL,4,Ccomplain to X over 'sickening' AI posts
OL,6,FHe said: "The hurt they will cause to
OL,7,Fthe families and survivors of those
OL,8,Finvolved in these tragedies will be
OL,9,Fimmense.
OL,11,F"The vast majority of fans will feel
OL,12,Fhorror and disgust at language like
OL,13,Fthis. It is deeply shocking that hate
OL,14,Ffilled content could be generated and
OL,15,Fcirculated by Grok on such a major
OL,16,Fplatform.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773137102
OL,3,CLiverpool and Manchester United
OL,4,Ccomplain to X over 'sickening' AI posts
OL,6,F"Technology companies have a clear
OL,7,Fmoral responsibility to ensure their
OL,8,Ftools do not produce or amplify abuse,
OL,9,Fand serious questions must be asked
OL,10,Fabout how this was allowed to happen."
OL,12,FThe Government has labelled the posts
OL,13,F"offensive and disappointing" and say
OL,14,Fthey go against "British values and
OL,15,Fdecency".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773137102
OL,3,CLiverpool and Manchester United
OL,4,Ccomplain to X over 'sickening' AI posts
OL,6,FA statement from the Department for
OL,7,FScience, Innovation and Technology
OL,8,Fwent on to say: "AI services including
OL,9,Fchatbots that enable users to share
OL,10,Fcontent are regulated under the Online
OL,11,FSafety Act and must prevent illegal
OL,12,Fcontent including hatred and abusive
OL,13,Fmaterial on their services. We will
OL,14,Fcontinue to act decisively where it's
OL,15,Fdeemed that AI services are not doing
OL,16,Fenough to ensure safe user
OL,17,Fexperiences."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
